section.div: Computational science Postdoc at Argonne National Laboratory working on applying machine learning to simulations in lattice QCD.
This repository implements and evaluates convolutional networks on the Mbius strip as toy model instantiations of Coordinate Independent Convolutional Networks.
This is the official repository to the WACV 2021 paper "Same Same But DifferNet: Semi-Supervised Defect Detection with Normalizing Flows" by Marco Rudolph, Bastian Wandt and Bodo Rosenhahn.
